title: John Hall - Professor Lectures While High
description:
I&#039;m looking to clean up my computer and get this stuff off here.. this is fun for a bit of a laugh.

This is lecturer John Hall of the University of Florida during a class when he&#039;s obviously really really high on something.  The first video is the best - the second is the class later in the day I think.

These are original files that were hosted on the University server before they got taken down.  They&#039;re unedited, which means you&#039;ll have to sit through a lot to see the better parts.  It&#039;s also fun to watch the students looking at each other awkwardly during this professor&#039;s escapades..

I think the second video of this is on Google video, but the first video got removed.

Anyhow, download this and spread it around..
